---
import { ArrowRight, Search, Zap } from "lucide-react";
import { Button } from "../ui/button";
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative pt-16 pb-24 overflow-hidden bg-background">
  <div class="container relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8 text-center">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground text-sm font-semibold animate-fade-in"
      >
        <Zap className="w-4 h-4 mr-2" />
        AIが最安値を24時間監視中
      </div>
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-foreground tracking-tight leading-[1.1]"
      >
        欲しいものを、<br />
        <span class="text-foreground"> 圧倒的に安く手に入れる。 </span>
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl leading-relaxed animate-slide-up"
      >
        UMUOは、Amazon、楽天、Yahoo!の価格を一瞬で比較。<br
          class="hidden md:block"
        />
        学生や社会人のための、最強のショッピングアシスタントです。
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <Button
          asChild
          size="lg"
          className="w-full sm:w-auto group rounded-2xl shadow-sm"
        >
          <a href="#products">
            <Search
              className="w-5 h-5 mr-2 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            />
            今すぐ商品を検索
          </a>
        </Button>
        <Button
          asChild
          variant="outline"
          size="lg"
          className="w-full sm:w-auto rounded-2xl bg-background/50 backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
          <a href="/deals">
            セール情報をチェック
            <ArrowRight className="w-5 h-5 ml-2" />
          </a>
        </Button>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust Badges -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 opacity-60 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500"
      >
        <span class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-gray-400"
          >SUPPORTED BY</span
        >
        <span class="font-black text-lg italic">Amazon</span>
        <span class="font-black text-lg text-red-600">Rakuten</span>
        <span class="font-black text-lg text-red-500">Yahoo!</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
